Paper: hep-th/9712012

Date: 1997-11-30

Title: String Dualities from Matrix Theory

Comments: 7 pages, Talk given at STRINGS'97

Journal-ref: Nucl.Phys.Proc.Suppl. 68 (1998) 374-380

I review the appearance, within Matrix theory, of the $SL(5,Z)$ U-dualitygroup of M-theory on $T^4$, and the duality between M-theory on K3 and theHeterotic string on $T^3$. In both cases the duality is geometrical andmanifest.